@HostAddress = http://localhost:5050
@FirebaseToken = REPLACE_WITH_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN

### Session (requires Firebase token)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{FirebaseToken}}

### Users list
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{FirebaseToken}}

### Dispatch notification
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/notifications/dispatch
Authorization: Bearer {{FirebaseToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

